
		  A Scenario for Microprose Civilization II

			      "East Wind, Rain"

	    (The Pacific War -- December 1941 to September 1945)

			  Version 1.2.0, 1996 May 05


EASTWIND.DOC: Table of Contents
-------------------------------
1. Description
2. Installation *** IMPORTANT - Please read about RULES.TXT! ***
